sub_title: Open for a job in project management and coordination
summary:
Results-driven professional with a diverse background in operations, customer service, and project management. I excel in optimizing processes, delivering exceptional customer experiences, and balancing the needs of both B2B and B2C stakeholders. With a data-driven approach, I identify areas for improvement and implement strategic solutions to drive business success.

I bring strong communication skills, expertise in case management, and a track record of exceeding targets in customer support. Additionally, my teaching background equips me with the ability to create engaging learning experiences and build strong relationships. I am now seeking opportunities to apply my skills in operations management, customer service, and project coordination to make a significant impact on business success.
